ork Times. As Winters experienced early stages of a pulmonary embolism, a potentially life-threatening blood clot in the lungs, he turned\u00a0to ChatGPT for advice.\u00a0Using ChatGPT-4o, released in May 2024, Winters initially received recommendations to seek professional medical care. But according to the lawsuit, those warnings stopped providing disclaimers as the conversations continued. Medical AI researcher Dr. Adam Rodman described the allegations as a \u201cnightmare scenario.\u201dThe lawsuit alleges ChatGPT eventually told Winters that his symptoms were \u201cnot something dangerous\u201d and that \u201cGod did not design your body to endlessly fail.\u201d\u00a0As Winters began experi", "large_image": "exekI59skQ5jXVQc.png", "title": "A Pastor Asked ChatGPT For Medical Advice. It Didn\u2019t End Well."}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBzzARm4", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 12, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8742930, "raw_content": "", "author": "icehole3", "created": 1784800006084, "profile_picture": "dRc40oxyuTmd", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "UH60MAGA", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBzzARm4.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/iTPW1VnhZi9q.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/FYn2jpYIJhnY60AX.jpeg", "width": 640, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 432}], "blurhash": "UPPZx|9G_NkqOZNHRkRjMyIUWAxv%Mt6n#V@", "full_resolution": [432, 640]}, "title": "Free Puppies ", "last_comment_created": 1784801652642, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_im